Azure Application Insights is an application performance management (APM) tool used to monitor software applications.

Capabilities:

* Request tracking
* Exception monitoring
* User behavior analysis
* Dependency tracking

For example, a web app can identify slow API calls impacting user experience.

# Real-Life Use Case:
A real-life use case is SaaS platforms optimizing customer-facing applications.

# Real-Life Example:
Another example is identifying bottlenecks in enterprise applications.

Application Insights helps developers improve software reliability and performance.
